          "A tHIS supports the exchange and integration of health data and documents across different health care institutions such as hospitals, medical offices, rehabilitation centers, nursing homes, ambulatory nursing organizations, and personal environments like patients’ homes.",
          "A tHIS enables comprehensive, patient-centered care by providing access to a patient’s health information regardless of where the care was provided.",
          "A tHIS typically includes components such as transinstitutional electronic health records (EHRs).",
          "A tHIS typically includes master patient indexes (MPI) for unique patient identification across institutions.",
